  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provide Medical Care to Maya Women Artisans</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Healthcare is a human right, but it&apos;s not accessible in rural Guatemala -particularly for indigenous women. That&apos;s why we&apos;re working with our town&apos;s hospital to offer free medical care to Cojolya&apos;s 30 artisans. Through this partnership, we ensure our artisans can continue supporting their families at the loom and maintain our cultural textiles for future generations. With your support, we can further empower Maya women in their pursuit of fair wages, academic opportunities, and, now, healthcare.</narrative>
  </description>
